content: It worked!!! That's all I guess? If so, I'll push everything to GitHub. Can you please compile a final report for CTO Claude that I can copy/paste? Great job Claude! In your final report, can you please include this for improvement that would help me in the next ATLAS project? These are using cat commands in separate text boxes that can just be copied/pasted into terminal with the button to create files. This saves time and ensures accuracy. Also, add anything on your end that you think you could have done better. Overall, this was a great success! Thank you for your partnership and support!
